{"tid":182450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來選委部電腦淨係得名，三百萬選民部電腦就有晒個人資料","createTime":"2017-04-01T11:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T10:04:59.000Z","uid":42536,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe32d98e3c8a3d36049646ed660e00b9116478b","tid":182450,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h4TBOqB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh4TBOqB.jpg&h=7f722d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你1200選委部電腦就淨係得名（連身份證都對唔到，咁帶去做咩？）<br />\n380萬選民資料嘅電腦就有齊晒資料（都冇份投，又帶去做乜？）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係痴撚線，越來越信有陰謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n一人一信向私隱專員投訴<br />\n<a href=\"https://charlesmok.typeform.com/to/MdFa0v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcharlesmok.typeform.com%2Fto%2FMdFa0v&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=63537a27\" target=\"_blank\">https://charlesmok.typeform.com/to/MdFa0v</a>"},{"pid":"0a58c7f216867f3bf43349df64a0310618a7e292","tid":182450,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24eefbdbdc205fafdac6f0f42e51d102ec1612d5","tid":182450,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:19:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655fecf30055f3d909a7a702b60b1e50a2e3654d","tid":182450,"uid":61752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee3ad2ed205e2b2e3a524393ad1423f13ea20f7","tid":182450,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:10:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28076331c169de2e1d825a304c0